public class XbaseDatasetReader
extends DataObjectDirectoryReader

The XbaseDatasetReader is a DataObjectReader that can read .dbf data files contained in a single directory. The reader will iterate through the .dbf files in alphabetical order returning all features.

See the AbstractDirectoryReader class for examples on how to use directory readers.

Author:
Paul Austin
